00:37:50,625 --> 00:37:52,375
It also gives us an
identifiable matter...

764
00:37:52,375 --> 00:37:54,083
O'BRIEN:
Commander La Forge.

765
00:37:54,083 --> 00:37:55,291
What can I do
for you, Chief?

766
00:37:55,291 --> 00:37:57,041
Could you look
at the pattern buffers?

767
00:37:57,041 --> 00:37:58,959
Considering what's happened
I'm not sure the control systems

768
00:37:58,959 --> 00:38:00,417
