769
00:38:00,417 --> 00:38:02,291
(<i> Picard continues indistinctly)</i>

770
00:38:02,291 --> 00:38:04,375
Sure, sure.
Let's take a look.

771
00:38:10,500 --> 00:38:13,542
Computer, I am reading
anomalous variations

